{
  "info": {
    "name": "clean-resmapi",
    "description": "Restaurant management system backend — Tech Challenge Phase 2 (FIAP Pós Tech, Arquitetura e Desenvolvimento Java). Covers UserType, User, Restaurant, and MenuItem, built with Clean Architecture.\n\nRun folders top to bottom via the Collection Runner: UserType → User → Restaurant → MenuItem create/read/update the core records and chain their ids into collection variables; Error Scenarios exercises the documented 400/404/409 failure paths while that data still exists; Cleanup deletes everything at the end in FK-safe order (children before parents).",
